<i>noun</i>: 화젯거리 [화제꺼리/화젣꺼리], 화제 [화제], 화두 [화두], 토픽 [], 이야깃거리 [이야기꺼리/이야긷꺼리], 얘깃거리 [얘ː기꺼리/얘ː긷꺼리], 논제 [논제] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>화젯거리 [화제꺼리/화젣꺼리]</dt><br>
<dd>topic; subject; issue</dd><br>
<dd>이야깃거리가 될 만한 재료나 내용.</dd><br>
<dd>Material or content worth making into a story.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>화제 [화제]</dt><br>
<dd>1. title; name</dd><br>
<dd>이야기의 제목.</dd><br>
<dd>The title of a story.</dd><br>
<dd>2. topic; subject; issue</dd><br>
<dd>이야기할 만한 재료나 소재.</dd><br>
<dd>Material or content worth making into a story.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>화두 [화두]</dt><br>
<dd>1. topic; subject; talking point</dd><br>
<dd>이야기의 첫머리.</dd><br>
<dd>Literally meaning the head of a story, the topic of a conversation or speech, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. topic</dd><br>
<dd>관심을 두어 중요하게 생각하거나 이야기할 만한 것.</dd><br>
<dd>An important subject that is worth thinking or talking about with interest.</dd><br>
<dd>3. keyword</dd><br>
<dd>불교에서, 수행을 하는 사람이 깨달음을 얻기 위한 실마리로 삼는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>In Buddhism, literally meaning the head of a story, a word or phrase used by an ascetic as a clue to reach spiritual enlightenment.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>토픽 []</dt><br>
<dd>1. topic; title</dd><br>
<dd>이야기의 제목.</dd><br>
<dd>The title of a story.</dd><br>
<dd>2. topic; issue</dd><br>
<dd>이야기할 만한 재료나 내용.</dd><br>
<dd>The material or content that constitutes a story.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>이야깃거리 [이야기꺼리/이야긷꺼리]</dt><br>
<dd>topic; subject</dd><br>
<dd>이야기할 만한 재료나 소재.</dd><br>
<dd>A material or subject matter worth being told.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>얘깃거리 [얘ː기꺼리/얘ː긷꺼리]</dt><br>
<dd>subject of conversation; topic; something to talk about</dd><br>
<dd>이야기할 만한 재료나 내용.</dd><br>
<dd>Materials or contents worthy of being talked about.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>논제 [논제]</dt><br>
<dd>subject of discussion; topic; agenda</dd><br>
<dd>토론이나 논의의 주제.</dd><br>
<dd>The subject of a debate or discussion.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>